{
  "stem": "26142.13",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it turned out that, that the guy, that the sergeant, that was, that got the papers-- we had to have papers to get, to get away-- the officer signed the papers in time to, but he, he didn't want to give it to us.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We finished up the work at 3:00.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a, a train that was going 3:30.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I figured, I'm going to take that train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when it came the time, he, he refused to give it to us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we missed, we missed the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after we missed the train, he gave it, he gave it to me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then there was another train that was going around 5:00.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And here again, I, I recount my biggest stupidity that I did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I got on the train 5:00, on the next train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this was [INAUDIBLE] of Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, and I was traveling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I, I would have, I would have come to Debrecen an hour or two late into the holiday.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, and, and in my stupidity, I, in one of the stations, the train stopped.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I saw people going to the synagogues.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I walked, I walked out in, in entirely a strange city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I was never there, because I didn't want to desecrate the holiday of Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But what turned out was that the next day after I went into Debrecen, and, and I over, overstayed my, my, my 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and, and I took a chance on that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that was the last time I saw this brother with his children and his wife.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How much more would have been happier if I would have left and come in an hour late?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I look at it now, I see how stupid I was.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
